{
 "fragments": [
  {
   "begin": "0.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "8.160", 
   "id": "s000001", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Herr Pr\u00e4sident! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "8.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "11.560", 
   "id": "s000002", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Meine sehr verehrten Damen und Herren! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "11.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "22.360", 
   "id": "s000003", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "1980 musste meine Familie in einer Nacht-und-Nebel-Aktion aus der T\u00fcrkei nach Deutschland fliehen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "22.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "29.760", 
   "id": "s000004", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Als Gewerkschaftler stand mein Vater auf der Todesliste der t\u00fcrkischen Milit\u00e4rjunta. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "29.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "31.320", 
   "id": "s000005", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ich wei\u00df also, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "31.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "34.480", 
   "id": "s000006", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "was Flucht bedeutet. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "34.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "39.920", 
   "id": "s000007", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Jetzt bin ich Mitglied des Deutschen Bundestages und sitze im Entwicklungsausschuss. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "39.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "51.040", 
   "id": "s000008", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das ist f\u00fcr mich eine Herzensangelegenheit."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "51.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "53.440", 
   "id": "s000009", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die Bundesregierung r\u00fchmt sich damit, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "53.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "59.920", 
   "id": "s000010", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "0,7\u00a0Prozent des Bruttoinlandsproduktes f\u00fcr die Entwicklungsarbeit auszugeben. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "59.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "63.000", 
   "id": "s000011", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Doch das ist Augenwischerei; "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "63.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "71.760", 
   "id": "s000012", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "denn ein Viertel der deutschen Entwicklungsgelder wird f\u00fcr die Versorgung von Gefl\u00fcchteten in Deutschland eingesetzt. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "71.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "74.000", 
   "id": "s000013", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Rechnet man diese Summe heraus, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "74.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "80.640", 
   "id": "s000014", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "betragen die Mittel f\u00fcr Entwicklungszusammenarbeit nur noch 0,5\u00a0Prozent. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "80.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "82.760", 
   "id": "s000015", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das ist ein Armutszeugnis."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "82.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "83.280", 
   "id": "s000016", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Frau Kollegin, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "83.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "85.360", 
   "id": "s000017", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "erlauben Sie mir eine kurze Unterbrechung. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "85.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "91.680", 
   "id": "s000018", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ich bitte die Kollegen der AfD-Fraktion, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "91.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "102.080", 
   "id": "s000019", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die Diskussion schon aus H\u00f6flichkeitsgr\u00fcnden zu unterlassen und entweder der Rednerin zuzuh\u00f6ren oder die Diskussion nach drau\u00dfen zu verlagern."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "102.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "102.600", 
   "id": "s000020", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Danke sch\u00f6n, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "102.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "105.840", 
   "id": "s000021", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Herr Pr\u00e4sident.\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "105.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "110.440", 
   "id": "s000022", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir Linke wollen die Entwicklungszusammenarbeit neu ausrichten. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "110.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "116.920", 
   "id": "s000023", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die Bed\u00fcrfnisse der Menschen in den Partnerl\u00e4ndern m\u00fcssen im Vordergrund stehen und nicht die sicherheits- "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "116.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "120.280", 
   "id": "s000024", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und wirtschaftspolitischen Interessen der Geberl\u00e4nder."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "120.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "125.600", 
   "id": "s000025", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die Entwicklungspolitik\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "125.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "127.720", 
   "id": "s000026", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "vor allem die linke Entwicklungspolitik\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "127.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "129.760", 
   "id": "s000027", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "baut auf drei S\u00e4ulen auf. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "129.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "132.880", 
   "id": "s000028", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir wollen erstens einen gerechten Welthandel, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "132.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "139.840", 
   "id": "s000029", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "zweitens den Klimawandel bek\u00e4mpfen und drittens eine friedliche Au\u00dfenpolitik. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "139.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "148.800", 
   "id": "s000030", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Eine gerechtere Welt muss auf einem gerechten Welthandel beruhen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "148.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "150.480", 
   "id": "s000031", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Man kann doch nicht sagen: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "150.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "151.320", 
   "id": "s000032", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Fein, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "151.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "153.000", 
   "id": "s000033", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "du bekommst Unterst\u00fctzung, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "153.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "153.840", 
   "id": "s000034", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "aber nur, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "153.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "157.480", 
   "id": "s000035", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wenn du unsere Produkte kaufst.\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "157.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "159.160", 
   "id": "s000036", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das ist doch keine Hilfe, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "159.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "164.240", 
   "id": "s000037", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die die wirtschaftliche Situation in den betroffenen L\u00e4ndern nachhaltig verbessert. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "164.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "168.880", 
   "id": "s000038", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Deswegen lehnt die Linke solche neoliberalen Abkommen strikt ab."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "168.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "180.040", 
   "id": "s000039", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Eine nachhaltige Entwicklungszusammenarbeit muss den Klimawandel wirksam bek\u00e4mpfen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "180.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "181.000", 
   "id": "s000040", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ich hoffe, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "181.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "183.080", 
   "id": "s000041", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sie konnten heute alle sch\u00f6n duschen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "183.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "183.960", 
   "id": "s000042", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Kaffee trinken, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "183.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "185.320", 
   "id": "s000043", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "sich die H\u00e4nde waschen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "185.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "187.040", 
   "id": "s000044", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das finde ich auch ganz gut."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "187.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "194.120", 
   "id": "s000045", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Jeder von uns verbraucht etwa 120\u00a0Liter Wasser t\u00e4glich. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "194.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "195.760", 
   "id": "s000046", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Es ist unvorstellbar, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "195.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "197.360", 
   "id": "s000047", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass es Menschen gibt, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "197.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "200.800", 
   "id": "s000048", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die 24\u00a0Stunden zu Fu\u00df unterwegs sind, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "200.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "202.440", 
   "id": "s000049", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "um Wasser zu holen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "202.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "205.880", 
   "id": "s000050", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "In den meisten F\u00e4llen ist es verseuchtes Wasser. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "205.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "212.960", 
   "id": "s000051", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Jeden Tag sterben fast 1\u00a0000\u00a0Kinder unter f\u00fcnf Jahren an den Folgen von schmutzigem Wasser. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "212.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "215.040", 
   "id": "s000052", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Schuld daran sind auch wir, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "215.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "219.440", 
   "id": "s000053", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die den Klimawandel verantworten und nichts dagegen tun. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "219.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "224.680", 
   "id": "s000054", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "\u00dcbrigens ist morgen der internationale Weltwassertag. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "224.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "226.360", 
   "id": "s000055", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Vielleicht denken Sie einmal daran, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "226.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "228.160", 
   "id": "s000056", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wenn Sie sich die H\u00e4nde waschen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "228.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "228.360", 
   "id": "s000057", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Last, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "228.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "239.960", 
   "id": "s000058", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "but not least kann eine erfolgreiche Entwicklungspolitik nur mit einer friedlichen Au\u00dfenpolitik funktionieren."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "239.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "245.280", 
   "id": "s000059", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Meine Damen und Herren, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "245.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "249.160", 
   "id": "s000060", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "ich habe Freunde in den umk\u00e4mpften Gebieten in Syrien, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "249.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "251.680", 
   "id": "s000061", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und sie berichten mir Schreckliches. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "251.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "262.040", 
   "id": "s000062", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sie sind Opfer des Staatsterrors des \u00adAssad-Regimes in Ost-Ghuta oder des v\u00f6lkerrechtswidrigen Angriffskriegs der T\u00fcrkei gegen die Kurden in \u00adAfrin. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "262.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "263.840", 
   "id": "s000063", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Und was macht die Bundesregierung? "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "263.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "266.560", 
   "id": "s000064", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sie militarisiert ihre Entwicklungspolitik. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "266.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "271.760", 
   "id": "s000065", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sie koppelt die Ausgaben f\u00fcr R\u00fcstung an die Ausgaben f\u00fcr Entwicklung: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "271.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "273.920", 
   "id": "s000066", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "je mehr R\u00fcstungsausgaben, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "273.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "278.480", 
   "id": "s000067", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "desto mehr Geld f\u00fcr Entwicklungshilfe also. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "278.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "283.920", 
   "id": "s000068", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das hat doch mit einer friedlichen Au\u00dfenpolitik gar nichts zu tun, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "283.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "284.720", 
   "id": "s000069", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "meine Damen und Herren."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "284.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "288.640", 
   "id": "s000070", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die Bundesregierung finanziert Kriege und will dann den Opfern scheinheilig helfen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "288.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "292.840", 
   "id": "s000071", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "um das eigene Gewissen gewisserma\u00dfen zu erleichtern\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "292.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "293.960", 
   "id": "s000072", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "mehr ist das nicht\u00a0\u2013, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "293.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "298.760", 
   "id": "s000073", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und dann liefert Deutschland munter weiter Waffen an Konfliktparteien. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "298.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "309.960", 
   "id": "s000074", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ausgerechnet das Volumen der Genehmigungen f\u00fcr R\u00fcstungsexporte in Entwicklungsl\u00e4nder hat sich 2017 auf \u00fcber 1\u00a0Milliarde Euro verdoppelt."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "309.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "311.360", 
   "id": "s000075", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Meine Damen und Herren, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "311.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "317.360", 
   "id": "s000076", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die Bundesregierung redet oft und gern von westlichen Werten, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "317.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "318.280", 
   "id": "s000077", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "von Demokratie, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "318.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "320.120", 
   "id": "s000078", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "von Frauenrechten. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "320.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "320.960", 
   "id": "s000079", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ja, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "320.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "323.400", 
   "id": "s000080", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die Kurden stehen f\u00fcr diese Rechte. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "323.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "327.360", 
   "id": "s000081", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die Bundesregierung aber bek\u00e4mpft die Kurden, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "327.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "328.240", 
   "id": "s000082", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
