   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "328.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "333.520", 
   "id": "s000083", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die f\u00fcr die westlichen Werte stehen und in der Anti-IS-Koalition gegen den IS k\u00e4mpfen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "333.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "334.880", 
   "id": "s000084", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "indirekt. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "334.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "336.240", 
   "id": "s000085", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das ist paradox, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "336.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "339.840", 
   "id": "s000086", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und die Bundesregierung sollte sich daf\u00fcr eigentlich sch\u00e4men."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "339.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "344.960", 
   "id": "s000087", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das sagt \u00fcbrigens eine, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "344.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "350.680", 
   "id": "s000088", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die selbst vor einem m\u00f6rderischen Milit\u00e4rregime aus der T\u00fcrkei fl\u00fcchten musste."
   ]
  }, 
